data.text: All in very good to fine condition. In this grouping is Melvin Calvin, dated signature; 1961 (Chemistry) -Francis Crick, signature; 1962 (physiology or medicine) -Thomas Cech, signature; 1989 (chemistry) -Jean Dausset, signed greeting; 1980 (physiology or medicine) - Werner Arber, signed greeting; 1978 (physiology or medicine) -Ernst Chain, signed greeting; 1945 (physiology or medicine) - Daniel Bovet, dated signature; 1957 (physiology or medicine) - Manfred Eigen, signed greeting; 1967 (chemistry) - George Beadle, signature; 1958 (physiology or medicine) b-Frank Burnet, singed greeting; 1960 (physiology or medicine) - Baruch Blumberg, two signatures; 1976 (physiology or medicine) - Donald Cram, signed greeting card; 1987 (chemistry) - Julius Axelrod, two signatures; 1970 (physiology or medicine) - Konrad Bloch, signed and dated greeting; 1964 (physiology or medicine). Near fine. Item #993
